	 * in trunk: <b>Replaced by {@link Wakka::authenticateUserFromCookies()},
	 * {@link Wakka::existsUser()} or {@link Wakka::loadUserData()} depending on
	 * purpose!</b>
	 *
	 * @param $name
	 * @param $password
